" - [#3]: [Imiloa](http://www.imiloahawaii.org/71/star-paths)\n"
" - [#4]: [Hawaiian Star Lines and Names for Stars](http://archive.hokulea.com/ike/hookele/hawaiian_star_lines.html)"
