" | Matamemea | Mars |\n"
" | Fetu'u | Star (in general) |\n"
" | Fetu'ufuka | Comet |\n"
" | 'Umata | Rainbow |\n"
" | Fetu'u'Esiafi | Falling star |\n"
" | Ma'afutoka (same as SMC) | Canopus |\n"
" | Ma'afulele (same as LMC) | Sirius |\n"
" | Velitoa hififo | Rigel |\n"
" | Velitoa hahake | Betelguese |\n"
" | Hikule'o | Arcturus |\n"
